        <prompt>What was the significance of the "Easter Monday" election riots?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Demonstrated violent resistance to black voting rights</option>
            <option letter="b">Led to increased voter turnout</option>
            <option letter="c">Improved election security</option>
            <option letter="d">Strengthened federal oversight</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Easter Monday election riots showed the violent resistance to African American voting rights and the difficulties in protecting black voters during Reconstruction.</explanation>
