    <question>
        <prompt>What was the impact of the "Georgia Returns" case?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Required Georgia to readmit black legislators</option>
            <option letter="b">Ended Reconstruction in Georgia</option>
            <option letter="c">Created new voting laws</option>
            <option letter="d">Established segregation</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Georgia Returns case forced Georgia to readmit black legislators who had been expelled from the state legislature, temporarily maintaining Reconstruction authority.</explanation>
